I for one, am LOVING the fact that I get a super awesome regen. It takes 1 mana to throw up (awesome for just being res'd), and takes mana away as it regens.. so slowly in fact that you can actually med.. and gain mana while regening!<br>
<br>
The DD is very very nice, too. I can now nuke mobs that aren't undead while they are coming in from pulls to keep the aggro on me.<br>
<br>
The 200hp buff is nice, I remember a few times where the extra 200hp would have saved my life. It's not a big deal, same difference as Symbol of Marzin is from Symbol of Naltron. Just more hp, that stacks. Look on the bright side, these are really nice new spells. <br>
<br>
The 15 second lifetap-for-damage is very nice too. I hit for well over 120, and believe me, the damage I do in 15 seconds would heal me quite a bit. That's about 5 swings, and up to 10 hits. Average hits.. 78. Let's say half of those 10 hit.. that's 400hp you just healed yourself. Worthless spell you say? <br>
<br>
The new disciplines.<br>
<br>
Resistance,.. ok, not so great, but nice to play around with while dealing with caster mobs.<br>
<br>
Fearless... good for those initial charges on dragons. Very good.<br>
<br>
Not sure what the other sk discs are, but they all have good uses, as long as you know when to use them.<br>
<br>
Just be happy, you may not have the &quot;uberest&quot; discs and spells, but you have another edge now. Might not be as sharp as some of the others, but at least you have something extra to throw in the fray now. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uarathena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arathena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dark Valkyrie of Innoruuk</span><br>  Posts: 287<br> <font color=#CC9900>(12/11/00 10:45:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The New spells.</span><hr size=1> Fenye, my only complaint at all is the Lvl 60 Discipline, if they actually jack the resistant up from +3s to everything.. For Innoruuk's sake, my DF helm does better than that, and I got that at 35, not lvl 52. Further, I said our Velious spells have promise. I like them. A lot. Our lvl 55 disc makes Harm touch pretty close to what it should be, lots of damage, and harder to resist. (It still won't touch things like dragons, Venril, etc. What, are they afraid someone will gather up 100 lvl 60 SKs and nuke  Naggy or Vox down? Ain't gonna happen, there might be 15 people with this disc on each server.)<br>
